Thanks to two of my favourites @mansidhamijachowdhary and @wowxmanish , I recently got a chance to great a charcoal and Pencil Portrait for the awe inspiring @masabagupta when they commissioned the same!
She inspires my generation with her body image positivity and zeal to live life on her terms and it resonates with me so well! 
From being this astounding Designer and then shocking everyone with her acting skills, you have pioneered your way with such grace! 

You are the “King” and the reigning “Queen” !!! 
I wish you nothing but success all through your life!
I hope this portrait brought you as much joy as it brought me making it!
@wowxmanish @mansidhamijachowdhary you guys have been nothing but generous and kind towards me and encouraged me always 😊Thank you immensely for that!

My love for textured art is ever growing!
Every layer tells a story; every texture holds a memory. Beneath the surface are the untold stories. Like relationships, depth is not seen, it’s felt and holds true for textured artworks.

Acrylic texture on canvas
“Beauty in Chaos”
3ft x 4ft
@the_unique_storyy 

DM for paid works

“Art is the only way to run away from home without leaving home”

Texture Art Painting

Texture in art is the perceived surface quality of a work of art. It can be perceived through the sense of touch, visually, or both. Implied texture gives the illusion of texture though the piece remains two-dimensional.
